    "Secondly, they consider the societal impact of AI as a critical component.",
    "Lastly, AI ethics is acknowledged as an essential aspect.",
    "These competencies collectively form the foundational elements of AI literacy, and they are consistently present as factors across the various scales.",
    "There is a consensus among the authors of the scales about the three competencies being essential for both secondary and higher education students as well as general population and medical professionals.",
